title: Manchester City star Jesus Navas joins team-mates in supercar brigade as he drives Porsche to training… as this time it’s Ilkay Gundogan who turns up in a Nissan
text:
EFL are you taking the niss? Manchester City star Jesus Navas joins team-mates in supercar brigade as he drives Porsche to training… as this time it’s Ilkay Gundogan who turns up in a Nissan 
Spanish winger Navas famously used to have a humble £8000 Nissan Micra... but German team-mate is the next City star to have a regular family car Pictured
